  "text": "However, the question of how during phases of urinary supersaturation stones develop on kidney calcifications and how this process can be prevented is not answered definitively [CITATION_1] . To get more information we studied the physiochemistry of crystallization [CITATION_2] and performed crystallization experiments on urine of stone formers (SF) and healthy controls (HC).",
